                box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.07);border:2px solid #f1f5f9;">
      <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:10px;">🛡️</div>
      <div style="font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:#1e293b;margin-bottom:6px;">Filtre Contenu Offensant</div>
