      <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:10px;">🌓</div>
      <div style="font-weight:800;font-size:16px;color:#1e293b;margin-bottom:6px;">Thème Adaptatif Ultra</div>
      <div style="font-size:13px;color:#64748b;margin-bottom:16px;">
        Détection OS automatique + persistance BDD + sync multi-appareils + 3 modes (Jour / Nuit / Auto).
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <span style="display:inline-block;background:#fef9c3;color:#854d0e;border-radius:20px;padding:4px 14px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;">
